    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers reliable transportation for someone seeking a practical, budget-conscious option. Mechanically, the engine and transmission perform as expected, though the car would benefit from a routine tune-up in the near future. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and staining, and a few plastic trim pieces are loose. It is a solid runner that gets you from point A to point B, but it is not a showpiece.",
