      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for exceptional volumetric efficiency. The power is delivered via a sought-after Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip M-Variable differential. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance: the rod bearings have been replaced, the VANOS system has been bulletproofed with uprated seals and hubs, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced with plates to eliminate the common chassis fatigue found in this generation. The suspension maintains its factory-spec kinematics with fresh bushings and dampers, ensuring the telepathic steering response the E46 is known for. No leaks, no codes, and a flawless underside.",
      "price": 44500.0,
